---
layout: default
title: FIRST Robotics
description: Supporting FIRST Robotics teams and fostering innovation in robotics education
---

<%= render Container.new(outer_class: "mt-16 sm:mt-32") do %>
  <header class="max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-800 sm:text-5xl dark:text-zinc-100">
      FIRST Robotics
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      Supporting FIRST Robotics teams and fostering innovation in robotics education through mentorship, resources, and community collaboration.
    </p>
  </header>
<% end %>

<%= render Container.new(outer_class: "mt-16 sm:mt-20") do %>
  <div class="space-y-20">

    <!-- About FIRST Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="flex text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none">
          <path d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909m-18 3.75h16.5a1.5 1.5 0 001.5-1.5V6a1.5 1.5 0 00-1.5-1.5H3.75A1.5 1.5 0 002.25 6v12a1.5 1.5 0 001.5 1.5zm10.5-11.25h.008v.008h-.008V8.25zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="ml-3">About FIRST</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-7 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          FIRST (For Inspiration and Recognition of Science and Technology) is a global robotics community that prepares young people for the future through a suite of inclusive, team-based robotics programs.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Robotics Collaborative is committed to supporting FIRST teams through mentorship, technical resources, and fostering connections within the robotics community.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Programs Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="flex text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none">
          <path d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="ml-3">FIRST Programs</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 p-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
              FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC)
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
              High school teams design, build, and program robots to compete in an annual game-based challenge.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 p-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
              FIRST Tech Challenge (FTC)
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
              Student teams design, build, program, and operate robots to compete in head-to-head challenges.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 p-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
              FIRST LEGO League (FLL)
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
              Elementary and middle school students research real-world problems and build LEGO-based robots.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 p-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">
              FIRST LEGO League Jr. (FLL Jr.)
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
              Ages 6-10 explore science and technology concepts through LEGO building and programming.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How We Support Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="flex text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none">
          <path d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="ml-3">How We Support Teams</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-7 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          The Robotics Collaborative provides comprehensive support to FIRST teams through various initiatives:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Technical mentorship from industry professionals</li>
          <li>Workshops on robot design, programming, and project management</li>
          <li>Access to tools, equipment, and fabrication resources</li>
          <li>Networking opportunities with other teams and mentors</li>
          <li>Scholarship and funding opportunities</li>
          <li>Career guidance and STEM education pathways</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Involved Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="flex text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none">
          <path d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="ml-3">Get Involved</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-7 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          Whether you're a student, educator, parent, or industry professional, there are many ways to get involved with FIRST and The Robotics Collaborative:
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2">For Teams</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>Register for mentorship programs</li>
              <li>Attend our workshops and training sessions</li>
              <li>Join our community forums and discussions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2">For Volunteers</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>Become a team mentor or coach</li>
              <li>Volunteer at competitions and events</li>
              <li>Share your expertise through workshops</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-100 p-6 dark:border-zinc-700/40">
      <h2 class="flex text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true" class="h-6 w-6 flex-none">
          <path d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="ml-3">Ready to Get Started?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        Contact us to learn more about how The Robotics Collaborative can support your FIRST team or to get involved as a volunteer.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 justify-center rounded-md py-2 px-3 text-sm outline-offset-2 transition active:transition-none bg-zinc-800 font-semibold text-zinc-100 hover:bg-zinc-700 active:bg-zinc-800 active:text-zinc-100/70 dark:bg-zinc-700 dark:hover:bg-zinc-600 dark:active:bg-zinc-700 dark:active:text-zinc-100/70">
          Contact Us
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true" class="h-4 w-4 stroke-zinc-100">
            <path d="M6.75 5.75 9.25 8l-2.5 2.25" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
<% end %>
